--------------------------------------------------------------------------------
  *. Environment in serverless.yml denotes Database credentials
  *. Profile in serverless.yml denotes respective bucket name where we need to store lambda functions

-------To run locally install these npm using these commands--------------------
  *. npm i servereless
  *. npm i serverless-offline

  *. And add this plug in serverless.yml file at last 
  -->  plugins:
           - serverless-offline

---------------------------------------------------------------------------------

--------To Deploy lambda functions in server-------------------------------------
   *. Remove serverless,serverless-offline packages from package.json
   *. Remove "serverless-offline" plugin from serverless.yml file
   *. use 'sls deploy' or 'serverless deploy' command to deployment
---------------------------------------------------------------------------------